# The Electron Shells · The electrons' quantized energy levels — shells K, L, M, N (n = 1, 2, 3, 4…), each holding up to 2n² electrons (2, 8, 18, 32), filled bottom-up under the Pauli exclusion principle. Held by the ELECTROMAGNETIC force.

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

